sentences.english: The Lord frustrates the plans of the nations and brings to nothing the peoples' designs.
sentences.chinese: 上主使異邦的計劃無緒，使萬民的策略廢去。

sentences.english: For Sagittarius it is most easily attracted by something from a foreign land.
sentences.chinese: 射手座最容易受到來自異邦事件的吸引。

sentences.english: To execute vengeance upon the nations, chastisements among the people.
sentences.chinese: 爲向異邦報仇雪恥，爲向列國進攻襲擊。

sentences.english: The police had captured a foreign spy.
sentences.chinese: 警方抓獲了一名異邦間諜。

sentences.english: Our inheritance is turned to aliens: our houses to strangers.
sentences.chinese: 我們的房舍，歸屬了異邦人。

sentences.english: She stood in tears amid the alien corn;
sentences.chinese: 使她不禁落淚，站在異邦的谷田裏想着家。

sentences.english: A large number of foreign companies have been the target of looting in the past month.
sentences.chinese: 昔日的一個月中，大量異邦公司成爲被洗劫的對象。
